<li>Among the proteins negatively regulated by CsgD , we could identify band 5 as a mixture of TnaA ( tryptophanase [ 22 ] ) and GatZ ( involved in galactitol-catabolism ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=17873038" target="_blank">17873038</a>]<br></li>
