<li>Role of the Bioﬁlm Master Regulator CsgD in Cross-Regulation between Bioﬁlm Formation and Flagellar Synthesis † Hiroshi Ogasawara ,1 Kaneyoshi Yamamoto ,1,2 and Akira Ishihama1 ,2 * Department of Frontier Bioscience1 and Research Center for Micro-Nano Technology ,2 Hosei University , Koganei , Tokyo 184-8584 , Japan Received 6 December 2010/Accepted 7 March 2011 CsgD , the master regulator of bioﬁlm formation , activates the synthesis of curli ﬁmbriae and extracellular polysaccharides in Escherichia coli .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=21421764" target="_blank">21421764</a>]<br></li>
